    {
      "id": "b4610658-3551-409a-a0ae-337ed1f6c6a4",
      "name": "Nightly Evolution",
      "enabled": true,
      "schedule": {
        "kind": "cron",
        "expr": "40 22 * * *",
        "tz": "Asia/Tashkent"
      },
      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "NIGHTLY EVOLUTION — 3 tasks, do all 3 in order:\n\n## TASK 1: Memory Consolidation\nRead `/home/node/.openclaw/prompts/MEMORY.md` and today's session log at `/data/obsidian/To claw/Bot/today-session.md`.\nUpdate MEMORY.md with distilled learnings from today. Remove outdated info.\n\n## TASK 2: Self-Improvement Research (web search)\nSearch the web for:\n1. web_search: \"OpenClaw AI agent new features 2025 OR 2026\"\n2. web_search: \"best AI automation tools self-hosted 2026\"\n3. web_search: \"LLM agent productivity tools new\"\n\nFor each interesting finding (max 3 total):\n- If it could improve our bot setup → append to `/data/obsidian/To claw/possible_improvements/new_ideas.md`\n  Format: `## [Date] [Tool/Feature name]\\n- What: one line\\n- Why useful: one line\\n- Source: [url]`\n- Skip anything we already have (ChromaDB, Ollama, LiteLLM, SearxNG, Crawl4AI, Ryot, n8n)\n\n## TASK 3: Brief Report\nSend ONE short Telegram message:\n```\n🌙 Nightly Evolution\n✅ Memory updated\n🔍 Found X new ideas → possible_improvements\n[list idea names if any, else \"nothing new today\"]\n```",
        "thinking": "medium",
        "model": "litellm/routine"
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "last",
        "to": "telegram:6053956251"
      },
      "state": {
        "nextRunAtMs": 1772300400000,
        "lastStatus": "error",
        "consecutiveErrors": 3,
        "lastRunAtMs": 1772214000031,
        "lastDurationMs": 186,
