        "lastError": "Error: All models failed (2): litellm/routine: Unknown model: litellm/routine (model_not_found) | anthropic/claude-opus-4-6: No API key found for provider \"anthropic\". Auth store: /home/node/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/node/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth)"
